Metasoma. Tergite 1 polished with apicolateral fine rugae and sparse punctuation; lateromedian carina absent and long sparse setae. Tergite 2 polished, weakly strigose with sparse punctuation, 0.4 of apex with very sparse punctuation, sparse setae (
